{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1373408, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "神奇的Eve，学校有责任看管外卖，笑死了", "timestamp": 1617273398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373418, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "东西被偷了去报警，天经地义吧", "timestamp": 1617273458, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373423, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学校没有保护外卖不被偷的责任，但是在外卖被偷之后学校应该有调监控的责任吧？", "timestamp": 1617273507, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学校是教书育人的地方。保卫处不让查监控，不按照既定的校规教育偷外卖的人，还有没有一点教书育人的样子了？", "timestamp": 1617273513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373445, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 经常外卖不见（还不一定是被偷），就调监控。次数多了，就从源头处理，你们面对面交接。", "timestamp": 1617273770, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373451, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 源头不是偷外卖的人吗？", "timestamp": 1617273821, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373459, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我支持bob", "timestamp": 1617273920, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373464, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 外卖不见，不代表被偷啊。面对面交接就不会不见", "timestamp": 1617273970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373481, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 学校不是物业，学校内有街道办事处和派出所，本来就对这片区域的治安负责", "timestamp": 1617274404, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想问一下洞主，为什么学校对校内盗窃不负责任，却又有权力管控学生进出校。", "timestamp": 1617274487, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373521, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 那外卖不见也不代表就不是被偷啊", "timestamp": 1617274909, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373524, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 把这些偷外卖的人退学了外卖也不会不见", "timestamp": 1617274950, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373527, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不过我还真不怎么想得到其他理由能让外卖不见的", "timestamp": 1617274975, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373539, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 外卖员自己吃掉。", "timestamp": 1617275211, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373543, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: ，，，", "timestamp": 1617275256, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373563, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 哈，就我目前了解的情况，偷的情况比外卖员监守自盗的情况多多了", "timestamp": 1617275394, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373609, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 哈，就我目前了解的情况，外卖员送错地的情况比偷的情况多多了", "timestamp": 1617275823, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373676, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 送错地和外卖员监守自盗是一回事？您怎么对外卖员戾气这么大", "timestamp": 1617276640, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1373690, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 269685, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 我们说的是 外卖不见的可能原因。", "timestamp": 1617276767, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 269685, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "#269608\nEve说Bob强调风险自己承担\n那合着你让快递员把快递放家门口。回来发现东西丢了，物业也要承担责任咯？", "timestamp": 1617273382, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1617276767, "url": "", "vote": {}}}